{"type": "article", "id": 2484, "title": "输液瓶式小型加湿器", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-22T08:39:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052325050vhyIw5H2rCt6eNs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t又笨又重的加湿器看多了，韩国设计团队11+ 带来了一款格调不俗的输液瓶式小型加湿器，让朴素的盐水瓶瞬间就变成了极富设计感的作品，它通过一条红色的 USB 线给瓶口的加湿装置供电，然后把瓶子内的水雾化出来，给生活或者工作空间增加空气湿毒。售价 60 美元，<a href=\"http://store.leibal.com/collections/11/products/11-bottle-humidifier-mini\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232504O5V6bWugk1wiEmLs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325046Lq9ZpoflybBmQEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232504mqyop86nHL3bcGkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232505AbOZVNWIaYKLU1BF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}